    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A base class for <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1RibbonMenuItem" kindref="compound">RibbonMenuItem</ref></computeroutput>s that can be toggled per viewport. The intent is that the derived classes should also be derived from <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1RibbonMenuItem" kindref="compound">RibbonMenuItem</ref></computeroutput> and be registered in the ribbon schema. Doing this ensures that you can loop over all items in the schema to get a list of all items toggleable in this way. </para>
